query:
SELECT id, error_type, severity, message, source, endpoint, occurrence_count, status, created_at 
FROM aec_detected_errors 
WHERE error_type = 'PAGE_NOT_FOUND'
ORDER BY created_at DESC 
LIMIT 3;
